        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;Join Donald A. Stuart and Susan Benson to hear the stories behind the Homage exhibition at this curator\\'s talk. Homage┬Āis a unique, beautiful and powerful exhibition of 40 tailor-made and [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
