        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;Saturday, May 2nd, 7:00pm. Entrance by donation. Join award-winning actor, producer, and storyteller Deb Williams at ArtSpring for a special performance of The FlameŌĆöVancouverŌĆÖs wildly popular live storytelling event. On [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
