  {
    "@id": "https://artspring.ca/temporary/8801ee7e-5639-4559-99eb-c3df864b95d0",
    "@type": [
      "https://schema.org/WebPage"
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom": [
      {
        "@id": "https://artspring.ca/event/the-flame-storytelling-slam-submissions-now-open/"
      }
    ],
    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t ┬½ All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tTHE FLAME STORYTELLING SLAM\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tMay 2, 2026 @ 7:00 pm - 9:00 pm\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\tEvent Series\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t(See All)\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSaturday, May 2nd, 7:00pm. Entrance by donation.\nJoin award-winning actor, producer, and storyteller Deb Williams at ArtSpring for a special performance of The FlameŌĆöVancouverŌĆÖs wildly popular live storytelling event.\nOn this night, ordinary people step onto the stage and do something extraordinary: they tell a true story from their own lives.\nJust six minutesŌĆ” and a story that matters.\nYouŌĆÖll hear stories that are funny, raw, unexpected, and deeply humanŌĆöstories that make you laugh out loud, catch your breath, and maybe even see yourself in someone elseŌĆÖs life.\nThis is storytelling at its simplestŌĆöand most powerful.\nStories have meaning.\nStories inspire us.\nMost importantly, stories bring us together.\nCome be part of a night where connection happens in real time.\nI dare you not to fall in love with the people on this stage.\nŌĆö Deb Williams\nThe Flame: True stories. Real voices.\nCALL FOR STORYTELLERS\nHave a story?\nA real one. About you.\nJoin us at ArtSpring for a special edition of The FlameŌĆöan unforgettable night of true stories told by the people who lived them.\nWeŌĆÖre inviting local storytellers (thatŌĆÖs you) to step up and share a 6-minute personal story in front of a live audience.\nJust you, your voice, and a story that matters.\nFunny, heartbreaking, awkward, triumphantŌĆöif itŌĆÖs true and it changed you (even a little), we want to hear it.\nYou donŌĆÖt have to be a performer.\nYou just have to be human.\nThis is what we do at The FlameŌĆöwe gather, we listen, we laugh, and tear up, we recognize ourselves in each other.\nWant to tell a story? Pitch me 250 words about your idea (beginning, middle and end) at: deb@theflame.live by Monday, April 27th. The theme is New Beginnings, and IŌĆÖll help you shape your story if needed.\nŌĆö Deb Williams\nThe Flame: True stories. Real voices.\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t May 2, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:00 pm - 9:00 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\tSeries: \n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tIGNITE: Advanced Storytelling Worksop for the Fearless Creator\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Categories: ArtSpring Presents 2025-26, Gallery Exhibits & Events\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t artspring.ca \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tArtSpring\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tAdd to calendar\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tGoogle Calendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tiCalendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook 365\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook Live\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t May 2, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:00 pm - 9:00 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\tSeries: \n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tIGNITE: Advanced Storytelling Worksop for the Fearless Creator\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Categories: ArtSpring Presents 2025-26, Gallery Exhibits & Events\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t artspring.ca \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tArtSpring\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\n\t\n    \n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Navigation\n\t\t\n\t\t\t┬½ IGNITE: Advanced Storytelling Workshop with Deb Williams\n\t\t\tIGNITE: Advanced Storytelling Workshop with Deb Williams ┬╗\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t"
