    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t ┬½ All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tSalt Spring Community Showcase\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tApril 17, 2026 @ 7:30 pm - 10:00 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t-\n\t\t\t\t\t\t$10 ŌĆō $30\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSalt Spring Community Showcase 2026, Live at ArtSpring ŌĆō April 17, 2026 | 7:30 PM\nOne night. Endless talent. All Salt Spring.\nGet ready for an unforgettable evening of creativity, passion, and performance as ArtSpring RoundTable proudly presents the Salt Spring Community Showcase ŌĆö a dynamic celebration of the artistic spirit that makes our island so extraordinary.┬Ā On April 17, 2026, the stage comes alive with an incredible array of local talent. Expect the wonderfully unexpected ŌĆö this one-night-only event brings together performers from all over Salt Spring to share their creativity in front of a live audience.\nThe Salt Spring Community Showcase spotlights the incredible creative voices in our own backyard. ItŌĆÖs a community celebration.\nFeaturing:\n-Wesley HardistyŌĆÖs traditional Northern, M├®tis, West Coast contemporary, and original instrumental fiddle music\n-Matthew McKinneyŌĆÖs musical storytelling\n-GISPA, with a scene from ŌĆ£The Little PrinceŌĆØ\n-Tangle McClaronŌĆÖs driftwood puppet theatre\n-Lisa MaxxŌĆÖs lullabies\n-Marilyn Walker & Edgar HannŌĆÖs celebration of Newfie and Irish music\n-With Grace Jordan on the mic as MC!\nJoin us for a magical night that puts a spotlight on who we are and what we create, together. If itŌĆÖs created on Salt Spring, it belongs on this stage.\nBUY TICKETS\n┬Ā\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t April 17, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:30 pm - 10:00 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $10 ŌĆō $30 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Categories: ArtSpring Presents, ArtSpring Presents 2025-26\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tAdd to calendar\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tGoogle Calendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tiCalendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook 365\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook Live\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t April 17, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:30 pm - 10:00 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $10 ŌĆō $30 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Categories: ArtSpring Presents, ArtSpring Presents 2025-26\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\n\t\n    \n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Navigation\n\t\t\n\t\t\t┬½ MAKANA YOUTH CHOIRS: Spring Term\n\t\t\tCancelled ŌĆō FIRE & GRACE ŌĆō Cancelled ┬╗\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t"
