        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;The Gulf Islands School of Performing Arts (GISPA) proudly presents The Little Prince, Adapted from Antoine de Saint-Exup├®ryŌĆÖs classic novel. The Little Prince upholds┬ĀGISPAŌĆÖs signature fusion of music, dance, and [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
