        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t ┬½ All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\tEvent Series:\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\tStageCoach Presents 2026 Year End Show\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tStageCoach: Lights Up! LetŌĆÖs Dance! Recital\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tApril 23, 2026 @ 6:30 pm - 7:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t-\n\t\t\t\t\t\t$5 ŌĆō $15\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t┬Ā\nStageCoach Theatre presents our year end dance show! Lights Up! LetŌĆÖs Dance!\nThe stage is set, the music is cued, and our dancers are ready to SHINE!\nJoin us for StagecoachŌĆÖs Year End Dance Showcase, April 23rd 6:30 PM\nThis high-energy celebration features performances from: Ballet 3ŌĆō5, 6ŌĆō8, Jazz 3ŌĆō5, 6ŌĆō8 & 9ŌĆō12 and our Performance Dance classes.\nFrom tiny twirls to powerful leaps, this showcase is a celebration of hard work, creativity, and a whole lot of heart. Our dancers have been building skills, confidence, and stage presence all season and now itŌĆÖs time to share it with you! Bring your cheers, your applause, and join us for a joyful night of music, dance and laughter.\nBe there April 23rd at 6:30 PM, you wonŌĆÖt want to miss it!\nBUY TICKETS\nApril 23 | 6:30pm | 1 hour | No Intermission ($15 adult, $5 youth)\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t April 23, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t6:30 pm - 7:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\tSeries: \n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tStageCoach Presents 2026 Year End Show\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $5 ŌĆō $15 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: Rental\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t stagecoachtheatre.ca \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t