    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t ┬½ All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tARROGANT WORMS\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tMarch 21, 2026 @ 7:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t-\n\t\t\t\t\t\t$10 ŌĆō $42\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSat Mar 21, 7:30pm | CanadaŌĆÖs kings of musical comedy are backŌĆöand still hilariously on point. For over 30 years, The Arrogant Worms have been poking fun at a big, weird world with razor-sharp wit and ridiculous charm. With cult hits like ŌĆ£Carrot Juice is MurderŌĆØ and ŌĆ£The Last Saskatchewan Pirate,ŌĆØ they built a devoted following in the ŌĆś90s, but theyŌĆÖre not just a nostalgia actŌĆötheyŌĆÖre still creating, touring, and making new generations laugh. Blending smart satire with musical chops, this trioŌĆÖs live shows are part stand-up, part folk concert, and 100% Canadian absurdity. Whether youŌĆÖre a longtime fan or discovering them for the first time, expect an evening of catchy tunes, clever comedy, and cathartic silliness. Still singing. Still yammering on. Still brilliant.\nBUY TICKETS\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t March 21, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $10 ŌĆō $42 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: ArtSpring Presents 2024-2025\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t ArtSpring ŌĆō Theatre \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n100 Jackson Avenue\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tSalt Spring Island,\n\n\tBC\n\n\tV8K 2V8\n\n\tCanada\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tPhone\n\t\t\t\t\t 250.537.2102 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tArtSpring\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\