        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t ┬½ All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tBALLET KELOWNA: Vividus ŌĆö Full of Life\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tMarch 23, 2026 @ 7:30 pm - 9:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t-\n\t\t\t\t\t\t$10 ŌĆō $42\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tMon Mar 23, 7:30pm | After opening ArtSpringŌĆÖs 25th Anniversary season to acclaim, Ballet Kelowna returns with Vividus: Full of LifeŌĆöa bold, high-energy program featuring three dazzling contemporary works by top Canadian choreographers. Alysa PiresŌĆÖ┬ĀVestiges is a sweeping, cinematic reflection on connection in a chaotic world.┬ĀThe Forever Part┬Āby Kirsten Wicklund offers a dreamlike meditation on longing, set to haunting ensemble movement. The evening concludes with Guillaume C├┤t├®ŌĆÖs whimsical and joy-filled┬ĀLe Carnaval des Animaux, a fresh, exuberant take on Saint-Sa├½nsŌĆÖ beloved score. Named 2024 Artistic Company of the Year, Ballet Kelowna continues to invigorate the national dance scene with power, precision, and play. A thrilling, accessible entry point for new audiencesŌĆöand a must-see for dance lovers.\nBUY TICKETS\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t March 23, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:30 pm - 9:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $10 ŌĆō $42 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Categories: ArtSpring Presents 2025-26, Dance\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t artspring.ca \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tArtSpring\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t ArtSpring ŌĆō Theatre \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n100 Jackson Avenue\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tSalt Spring 