        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;IMMERSIVE EXPERIENCE: A WEEKLONG RESIDENCY INCLUDING A FILM SCREENING AND CONCERT ArtSpring is proud to present Roots &amp; Wings, OstaraŌĆÖs new double album and performance experience. This deeply personal work [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
