      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t ┬½ All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tBuzz Brass: Famous Inspirations\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tJanuary 25, 2026 @ 2:30 pm - 4:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t-\n\t\t\t\t\t\t$10 ŌĆō $42\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSun Jan 25, 2:30pm | With flair, finesse, and fun, CanadaŌĆÖs renowned Buzz Brass quintet brings classical masterpieces into bold new focus. In Famous Inspirations, the group reimagines beloved works by Debussy, Ravel, Piazzolla, Dvo┼Ö├Īk, and LisztŌĆöincluding the iconic Hungarian Rhapsody No. 2 ŌĆöthrough dazzling original arrangements. These turn-of-the-century classics are transformed through the brilliance of brass, highlighting fresh textures, rhythms, and colours youŌĆÖve never heard before. Known for their virtuosity, dynamic stage presence, and genre-crossing creativity, Buzz Brass has performed over 2,000 concerts across three continents and earned acclaim from CBC Music as a ŌĆ£top-notch brass quintet.ŌĆØ This is a concert that will appeal to classical fans, first-timers, and everyone in between. Prepare to be surprised and thoroughly entertained.\nBUY TICKETS\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t January 25, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2:30 pm - 4:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $10 ŌĆō $42 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: ArtSpring Presents 2025-26\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t artspring.ca \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tArtSpring\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t ArtSpring ŌĆō Theatre \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n100 Jackson Avenue\n\t\