    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t ┬½ All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\tEvent Series:\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\tGISS TheatreŌĆÖs Peter Pan\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tGISS TheatreŌĆÖs Peter Pan\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tJanuary 14, 2026 @ 7:30 pm - 9:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t-\n\t\t\t\t\t\t$15\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPeter Pan ŌĆō GISSŌĆÖs 2nd Story Theatre has been crafting an astounding new production of Peter PanŌĆöa dynamic, imaginative show you wonŌĆÖt want to miss. This marks only the second time Grade 9 students have appeared in a 2nd Story production, and the entire ensemble has been working tirelessly to bring this magical world to life for you.\nTravel with Peter Pan as he whisks Wendy, John, and Michael away to NeverlandŌĆöa place where childhood lasts forever, and every day is an adventure. Pirates lurk, mischief brews, and excitement fills the air. But when the infamous Captain Hook begins stirring up trouble, the stakes rise. Can the Lost Boys hold on to their sense of family? Or will Hook finally have his revenge on Peter?\nJoin us for this wonderful ride of laughter, suspense, and awe as we journey back to the boundless imagination of childhood. This show has been entirely designed and produced by the students.\nIntermission | Concession | 2 Hours | $15 General ticket\nBUY TICKETS\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t January 14, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:30 pm - 9:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\tSeries: \n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tGISS TheatreŌĆÖs Peter Pan\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $15 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: Rental\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\