        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t ┬½ All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tSSI Foundation Presents Understanding Family Generational Wealth\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tNovember 7, 2025 @ 3:00 pm - 6:00 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\nHear bestselling author Tom Deans speak about the Family Wealth Transfer movement and how to better understand your familyŌĆÖs generational wealth.\nOne of CanadaŌĆÖs preeminent thought leaders who has delivered over 2000 speeches globally, Dr. DeansŌĆÖ will share ideas from his engaging books including Every FamilyŌĆÖs Business, Willing Wisdom, and The Happy Inheritor.\nCanada is currently navigating the greatest wealth transfer in history, with baby boomers expected to pass on $1 trillion dollars in assets by 2026. Dr. Deans will shed light on why 15 million Canadians do not yet have a legal will, how to start your family wealth transfer conversation, and how families are inspired to navigate the $300 million inherited in Canada daily with charity and grace.\nCelebrating the power of philanthropy in community, youŌĆÖll also hear stories from local organizations about their impactful community work undertaken with the support of Salt Spring Island Foundation funding.\nPresented by Salt Spring Island Foundation, BMO Nesbitt Burns Private Wealth, and ArtSpring.\nREGISTER FOR YOUR FREE TICKET\n3 hours with intermission & concession\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t November 7, 2025 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3:00 pm - 6:00 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: Rental\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t ssifoundation.ca \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tSalt 