    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t ┬½ All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tTREASURE FAIR 2025\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tJuly 16, 2025 - July 19, 2025\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tJuly 16-19 | ArtSpringŌĆÖs biggest fundraiser of the year is back! ┬ĀHeadlined by a beautiful 2004 Steinway & Sons piano valued at over $68,000, Treasure Fair offers items and experiences at all price points. Furnishings, jewelry, artworks, musical instruments, sporting equipment, collectibles, professional services, and more. Last yearŌĆÖs Treasure Fair was ArtSpringŌĆÖs most successful yet, and weŌĆÖre looking to keep the momentum rolling.\nSupport ArtSpring in its mission to enrich, uplift, and connect our community through arts and culture.\nTO REGISTER for bidding and an invitation to the Sneak Peek Gala Event before bidding goes live: treasurefair.artspring.ca\nDONATE: If you wish to ┬Āvolunteer, please email treasure@artspring.ca\nKEY DATES:\nWed June 18: Last day for donations.\nWed July 2: Online Catalogue goes live.\nWed July 16: Treasure Fair Sneak Peek Gala for registrants and donors: 4pm-6pm\nWed July 16: Online bidding goes live: 6pm\nSat July 19: Bidding closes: 6pm\nFri July 18: Treasure Fair Concert: ZACHARY STEVENSONŌĆÖs ŌĆ£Dead Ringer.ŌĆØ A tribute to Buddy Holly, Hank Williams, Jerry Lee Lewis and other classics!\nBUY CONCERT TICKETS\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tStart:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t July 16, 2025 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tEnd:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t July 19, 2025 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: ArtSpring Presents 2024-2025\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t treasurefair.artspring.ca \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tArtSpring\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tAdd to calendar\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tGoogle Calendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tiCalendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook 365\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook Live\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tStart:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t July 16, 2025 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tEnd:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t July 19, 2025 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: ArtSpring Presents 2024-2025\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t treasurefair.artspring.ca \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tArtSpring\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\n\t\n    \n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Navigation\n\t\t\n\t\t\t┬½ Land & Lineage\n\t\t\tTREASURE FAIR CONCERT | ZACHARY STEVENSON ŌĆ£Dead RingerŌĆØ ┬╗\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t"
