  {
    "@id": "https://artspring.ca/temporary/33ef9afb-35c6-415c-9500-3014725ef07d",
    "@type": [
      "https://schema.org/WebPage"
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom": [
      {
        "@id": "https://artspring.ca/event/piano-heist/"
      }
    ],
    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t ┬½ All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tPIANO HEIST\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tApril 1, 2025 @ 7:30 pm - 9:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t-\n\t\t\t\t\t\t$5 ŌĆō $35\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\nAPR 1 | 7:30pm | Lifelong friends, colleagues, and multi-talented musicians Nico Rhodes and Patrick Courtin were shocked and appalled by their realization that piano just isnŌĆÖt cool anymore. This set off a quest to redeem the keyboard and reinstate its reputation as the greatest instrument of ALL TIME! \n\n\nArmed with the music of the greatest composers, songwriters, and performers of the past 300 years, and the technology of the 21st century ŌĆō Nico and Patrick deliver everything from classical piano raptures and bombastic boogie woogie to romantic piano ballads and 80ŌĆÖs keyboard synth as they battle it out in their show Piano Heist! What ensues is a mishmash of theatrical wonder, comedy, audience participation, heartfelt stories, a pinch of history, and a world of musical madness.\n\n\nThank you to Kate Merry for sponsoring this performance.\nBUY TICKETS\nACT ONE\nBACH TO THE BEGINNING\n┬ĀMinuet in G major ŌĆō J.S. Bach\n┬ĀGoldberg Variations No.1 ŌĆō J.S. Bach\n┬ĀToccata and Fugue ŌĆō J.S. Bach\n┬ĀPhantom of the Opera ŌĆō A.L. Webber\n┬ĀHit the Road Jack ŌĆō Ray Charles\n┬ĀIn the Hall of the Mountain King ŌĆō Edvard Grieg\n┬ĀImperial March ŌĆō John Williams\n┬ĀHabanera (Carmen) ŌĆō Georges Bizet\n┬ĀJurassic Park ŌĆō John Williams\n┬ĀSir Duke ŌĆō Stevie Wonder\n┬ĀHockey Night in Canada ŌĆō Dolores Claman\nDJ LUDWIG\n┬ĀSonata No.16 in C Major ŌĆō Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart\n┬ĀF├╝r Elise ŌĆō Ludwig van Beethoven\n┬ĀFantasie Impromptu ŌĆō Fr├®d├®ric Chopin\n┬ĀGymnopedies ŌĆōErik Satie\n┬ĀHungarian Dance n.6 ŌĆō Johannes Brahms\n┬ĀRhapsody in Blue ŌĆō Georges Gershwin\n┬ĀHungarian Rhapsody n.2 ŌĆō Franz Liszt\nTWO NIGHTS WITH CHOPIN\n┬ĀNocturne No.2 in Eb ŌĆō Fr├®d├®ric Chopin\n┬ĀFreddieŌĆÖs Rag ŌĆō Rhodes/Chopin\nAND ALL THAT JAZZ!\nSing, Sing, Sing ŌĆō Benny Goodman\nMoondance ŌĆō Van Morrison\nI donŌĆÖt mean anything ŌĆō Duke Ellington\n┬ĀBlue Rondo a la Turk ŌĆō Brubeck\nLand of the Misty Giants ŌĆō Oscar Peterson\n┬ĀA Date with An Improvisation ŌĆō Nico Rhodes\nSO, YOU THINK YOU CAN DANCE?\n┬ĀTico Tico ŌĆō┬Ā┬Ā Zequinha de Abreu\nINTERMISSION\nACT TWO\nFRIGHT OF THE BUMBLE BEE\n┬ĀIf I Only Had a Brain ŌĆō Arlen\n┬ĀBumble Bee Boogie ŌĆō Korsakov/Rhodes\n┬ĀEye of the Tiger ŌĆō Survivor\nCHEERS TO THE PIANO PEOPLE\n┬ĀGreat balls of fire ŌĆō Otis Blackwell/Jack Hammer\n┬ĀWhatŌĆÖd I Say ŌĆō Ray Charles\n┬ĀGreen onions ŌĆō Booker T and the MGŌĆÖS\n┬ĀHouse of the Rising Sun ŌĆō Georgia Turner/Bert Martin\n┬ĀLight my fire ŌĆō The Doors\n┬ĀHey Jude ŌĆō The Beatles\n┬ĀTiny Dancer ŌĆō Elton John\n┬ĀCrocodile Rock- Elton John\n┬ĀSuperstition ŌĆō Stevie Wonder\n┬ĀPopcorn ŌĆō Gershon Kingsley\n┬ĀMoney ŌĆō Abba\n┬ĀThe final countdown ŌĆō Europe\nTHE BETRAYAL\n┬ĀClaire the Lonely ŌĆō Claude Debussy\n┬ĀJe vais Survivre ŌĆō Freddie Perren & Dino Fekaris\nSALOON BATTLE aka HOEDOWN ALLA TURCA\n┬ĀRondo Alla Turca ŌĆō Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart\nRHAPSODIC REUNION\n┬ĀBohemian Rhapsody ŌĆō Queen\nREVENGE OF THE GUITAR\nGuitar battle ŌĆō Nico Rhodes\nOde to Joy ŌĆō Ludwig van Beethoven\nKEYS ARE THE CHAMPIONS\nWe are the Champions ŌĆō Queen\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t April 1, 2025 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:30 pm - 9:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $5 ŌĆō $35 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: ArtSpring Presents 2024-2025\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tArtSpring\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t ArtSpring ŌĆō Theatre \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n100 Jackson Avenue\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tSalt Spring Island,\n\n\tBC\n\n\tV8K 2V8\n\n\tCanada\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t+ Google Map\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tPhone\n\t\t\t\t\t 250.537.2102 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tAdd to calendar\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tGoogle Calendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tiCalendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook 365\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook Live\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t April 1, 2025 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:30 pm - 9:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $5 ŌĆō $35 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: ArtSpring Presents 2024-2025\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tArtSpring\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t ArtSpring ŌĆō Theatre \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n100 Jackson Avenue\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tSalt Spring Island,\n\n\tBC\n\n\tV8K 2V8\n\n\tCanada\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t+ Google Map\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tPhone\n\t\t\t\t\t 250.537.2102 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\n\t\n    \n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Navigation\n\t\t\n\t\t\t┬½ JANINA FIALKOWSKA\n\t\t\tFemme Frequency: Lobby Exhibition ┬╗\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t"
